  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13102997/hero-family-900.jpg" alt="FamilyHero900" data-udi="umb://media/00c0a0d21ca443ac94ff809a59797d84" /></p>
<p><strong>Mountains of family fun</strong> - There is nothing quite like sharing a ski or snowboarding adventure holiday with your family. No matter your children's age, there is something very special about a holiday in the mountains. Be it practicing your turns together or whizzing down the slopes in competition - whatever level of skiing or snowboarding abilities you and your family have, Inghams has a winter getaway for you.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/814ee487007a4de8bf9a553648bd1a56" href="/{localLink:umb://document/814ee487007a4de8bf9a553648bd1a56}" title="Easter" class="c-btn">Easter ski deals</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/4e712db85df04efb8097192316f0e0bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4e712db85df04efb8097192316f0e0bb}" title="Half Term" class="c-btn">Half-term ski deals</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d}" title="Christmas" class="c-btn">Christmas deals</a></p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Childcare options</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Inghams doesn't directly offer dedicated childcare services in resort. However we can recommend a full list of options via hotels.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e0f33c40be46416cbb547a6f9e327b61" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0f33c40be46416cbb547a6f9e327b61}" class="c-btn">Read more here</a></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Family discount offers</h3>
<span style="font-size: 14px;">Save up to 50% on child places on selected hotels and chalets across Europe.</span>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/db7a2008a7c84902a4dc5ab441016bf6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/db7a2008a7c84902a4dc5ab441016bf6}" title="2024/25 Discounted child places" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">View offer here</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12"></div>
<h2>The best family ski resorts</h2>
<p>Some of Inghams favourite family friendly resorts across Europe:</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière">La Rosiere, France</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103013/valdisere-family-500x350.jpg" alt="ValDFamily500x350" data-udi="umb://media/93edcc27f5ca47799cf8bf82d673f421" /></p>
<ul>
<li>High-altitude resort with a good snow record and known to be a sunny stop</li>
<li>Plenty of Green and Blue slopes offering wide and gentle pistes</li>
<li>Offering partnerships with quality ski schools offering group or private lessons </li>
<li>Good selection of family friendly stays including hotels, chalets or apartments</li>
<li>Off-slope fun, from a cinema, bowling to ice skating</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" class="c-btn">La Rosiere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes, France</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103011/tignes-family-500x350.jpg" alt="TignesFamily500x350" data-udi="umb://media/47deed0d1ee14dbdb3ccb97ae6140987" /></p>
<ul>
<li>High-altitude resort with a handy free bus service</li>
<li>Top rated ski schools to chose from, mainly located by the start of the slopes<span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"></span></li>
<li>A beginners area near the resort and lots of cruisy, wide runs further up</li>
<li>Lots of space for fun afternoons of tobogganing or sledging</li>
<li>Good array of accommodation with on-site pools, restaurants or games rooms</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes" class="c-btn">Tignes</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686" href="/{localLink:umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686}" title="Champoluc">Champoluc, Italy</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102998/la-ros-family-500x350.jpg" alt="LaRos500x350" data-udi="umb://media/4c2852fc584a4b75a4c33f73242ed02d" /></p>
<ul>
<li>3 ski areas with one lift pass so you can explore all beginner areas</li>
<li>Pre-bookable ski schools in resort</li>
<li>Perfect for slightly more advanced or older children who want to explore on and off the slopes</li>
<li>A good mix of centrally based hotels - offering ski-in ski-out, spa facilities and a hearty breakfast. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686" href="/{localLink:umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686}" title="Champoluc" class="c-btn">Champoluc</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isere, France</a><span style="color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"></span></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103012/champoluc-family-500x350.jpg" alt="ChampolucFamily50x350" data-udi="umb://media/1e2f00f6890646bdbffc2a7bbb1b8e3c" /></p>
<ul>
<li>High-altitude resort, with free shuttle bus and connected to Tignes</li>
<li>In resort nursery slopes come with free lifts for the little ones</li>
<li>Dedicated beginners area at the top of Solaise lift</li>
<li>Perfect mix of family friendly accommodations, offering apartments, hotels and chalets</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere" class="c-btn">Val d'Isere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Best family friendly accommodation</h2>
<p>A selection of some of Inghams top choices for family accommodation </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3d336aa6ddd24ea9b4b57ccaf8abb958" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d336aa6ddd24ea9b4b57ccaf8abb958}" title="The Moss">The Moss Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090343/modd_latvany_25os-szoba_01.jpg" alt="themosshotel" data-udi="umb://media/b3300fad035742a588e3fd6d0c4eec2c" /></p>
<p><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">The hotel is located in a quiet side street only two minutes walk from the nearest piste and ski school meeting point.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl" class="c-btn">Obergurgl</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4398db286fbe4970b51fe8ef2aaaa2e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4398db286fbe4970b51fe8ef2aaaa2e4}" title="Lodge Hemera Apartments">Lodge Hemera Apartments</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13088034/lodge-hemera-reception_85.jpg" alt="LodgeHemera" data-udi="umb://media/ff76b15121324adabf478b9441a6812d" /></p>
<p><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">These apartments offer up to 3 bedroom spaces with a pool and communal lounge area. They are just a short walk to the ski lifts. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière" class="c-btn">La Rosiere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/05259756329d41158895b5406a6a7312" href="/{localLink:umb://document/05259756329d41158895b5406a6a7312}" title="Hotel Au Charmant Petit Lac">Hotel Au Charmant</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089884/charmant-petit-lac-59.jpg" alt="HotelCharmant" data-udi="umb://media/891670b006ab438eb87808bc6d26c746" /></p>
<p>This hotel has comfy rooms, a swimming pool and great Italian dishes, perfect for the kids. Its close to the resort centre.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686" href="/{localLink:umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686}" title="Champoluc" class="c-btn">Champoluc</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/71c9f06526254f03a4a3d53e17d19b41" href="/{localLink:umb://document/71c9f06526254f03a4a3d53e17d19b41}" title="Hotel Park">Hotel Park</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103036/hotel-park-saas-fee-winter-exterior-338x182.jpg" alt="HotelPlan" data-udi="umb://media/f915bf1639a8439ea555cf99f4e2d475" /></p>
<p>This is a family friendly, family run hotel in a quiet but central location - welcoming atmosphere and great food make this a great place.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee" class="c-btn">Saas Fee</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a974436a181a43c193afabccefad916d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a974436a181a43c193afabccefad916d}" title="Hotel Ducs De Savoie">Hotel Ducs de Savoie</a><strong><br /></strong></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13088114/ducs-de-savoie-lounge.jpg" alt="DucsDeSavoie" data-udi="umb://media/33bee29f1c024d6bbe9bcd0e2283ef04" /></p>
<p><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">This welcoming and cosy hotel was renovated in 2021 and has some great family room options. It is close to the resort centre.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere" class="c-btn">Val d'Isere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/6c619b8f56a14296bba3d4bad6690d24"><a data-udi="umb://document/6c619b8f56a14296bba3d4bad6690d24" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6c619b8f56a14296bba3d4bad6690d24}" title="Hotel Mareo">Hotel Mareo</a><strong><br /></strong></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13084674/hotel-mareo-outdoor-heated-pool.jpg" alt="HotelMareo" data-udi="umb://media/6d19c0a8cc1b4e9f909eb898b49a197a" /></p>
<p><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">For families with slightly older children who want the family room options but with a more sophisticated feel, this hotel is an ideal choice.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/23b9cedc49ac4fe3ab5c6bd3b0c4b1b0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/23b9cedc49ac4fe3ab5c6bd3b0c4b1b0}" title="Kronplatz" class="c-btn">Kronplatz</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">No Snow? S'no problem!</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Inghams Ski holidays are all covered by our Snow Guarantee</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Read more here:</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f4ae07b2d50a4681918f9b4a3d6500c6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f4ae07b2d50a4681918f9b4a3d6500c6}" title="Snow Guarantee" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Snow Guarantee</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>When to go on a family ski holiday</h2>
<p>We offer some great family holiday options for skiing and snowboarding around the school holidays</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Easter Family Ski Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13093313/easter.jpg" alt="skieaster" data-udi="umb://media/3cfcf3303d4f45fcae565f011bb4f805" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5cafb4722ba54fe9acbeb514514e8354" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cafb4722ba54fe9acbeb514514e8354}" title="Easter Skiing" class="c-btn">Easter skiing</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Half Term Ski Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13093314/half-term.jpg" alt="halfterm" data-udi="umb://media/17ce482174c0443a8cad9a194aa9ead2" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7d4f46abfb6a4bc999ea4fcfc363cdf0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d4f46abfb6a4bc999ea4fcfc363cdf0}" title="Half-Term skiing" class="c-btn">Half-term skiing</a></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Festive Family Ski Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13093315/fireworks.jpg" alt="fireworks" data-udi="umb://media/282e00d3a3eb48d68249358d482e8a80" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee}" title="Christmas Skiing" class="c-btn">Festive skiing</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Family skiing FAQs </h2>
<p><strong>How do I plan a family Ski holiday?</strong> - Firstly, it is best to check your children's term dates, then it is advisable to look at the country you ideally want to visit compared to the airport you wish to depart from. It is always best to scope out the types of accommodation in your desired destination to make sure there are family friendly options. We would suggest using our Search Bar at the top of our website where you can search by Destination, Date, Guests and Airport.</p>
<p><strong>What do I pack for a family?</strong> - Lots of layers, keeping warm is all about layering up. We have a great <a data-udi="umb://document/5effa980d89944338f4e4de90c924c1c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5effa980d89944338f4e4de90c924c1c}" title="Insider's Guide: A Beginner’s Guide to What to Wear Skiing">Insider's Guide</a> where you can get a more in-depth understanding of what is needed while skiing.</p>
<p><strong>What to do as a family of new skiers?</strong> - We would certainly recommend booking yourself some lessons with the local ski schools, children and adults alike and to also make use of the practice parks and play areas.</p>
<p><strong>Can parents have adult ski time only?</strong> - You can make the most of on-site ski schools at many resorts so that you can have time to ski freely or enjoy a leisurely lunch.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
